	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ok here is my take.<br><br>I was there with 2 friends (55 Druid - 56 Druid - 56 Wiz).&nbsp;&nbsp;This Guy Summons - very often so be careful. He also Dispels, and nukes. His nukes were not extreme - ranged from 200 to 300 hp nukes.  He moves quite slow and snare landed on first try, but with his constant summoning it makes no diference IMHO.  Root stuck well also, but once again... the darn summoning.  Well IMHO opinion again, a balanced group - with a tank and cleric should have no real problems with this guy at around levels 55 and probably lower also, since we were quite inexperienced with this zone and didnt even expect him to be a summoning mob.  His mellee was around 140 (if i remember this correctly). Unfortunately due to the constant summoning I had to look for a cleric later so I cant talk about his loot really.<br><br>Good Luck with him, I hope this info helped a bit.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
